summary: Were you ever bothered by that chin form elfs that could have sunk the titanic? This preset could definitely save you some work :)
descriptionHtml:
I was a bit bugged by the chin from woodelfs... i mean, that chin definitely looks like it was the fault that the titanic sunk. :P
So here she is:
[size=3][b]My female Bosmer Sri'Leyah. [/b][/size]
Hope you guys like her!

I'm sorry for the "bad" quality of the newer Screenshots... i did them for myself and my Skyrim is not that highly modded in Textures :/

[b]Requirements:[/b]
[list]
[*][url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url] by Expired
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes Of Beauty[/url] by Gabriel Mailhot
[/list][list]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?]ApachiiSkyHair (ApachiiHairFemales)[/url] by Apachii
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50032/?]KJ Tattoos - Overlay Plugins for RaceMenu[/url] by Khajiitas (Only required for Main File)
[/list]


[b]How to install: (I'll only do MO 'cause i only know how it works for it)[/b]
For MO, just take the ".jslot" into the folder "Presets".
Go into showracemenu/Start a new Game,
Set race to Woodelf (and gender to female obviously) and go to the presets tab, hit F9 to load a preset.
Select the one called "Sri'Leyah.jslot" and hit enter.
Enjoy!
[b]
Mods in Screenshot(applies only for 1_0 screenshots):[/b]
[list]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35352/?][/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30936/?]RealVision ENB[/url] by [b]SkyrimTuner[/b]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/74702/?]VS Medieval Archeress Dress [/url]by ViciousSARR
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29123/?]Transparent and refracting Glass Eqmnt CBBE UNP UNPB [/url]by Skysan4298
[/list]
[b]
Credits:[/b]

The Eyes Of Beauty by Gabriel Mailhot

ApachiiSkyHair by Apachii
VS Medieval Archeress Dress by ViciousSARR
My Friend Aldreac who made some of those Screenshots for me

files.changelogHtml:

3. Smothed the area aorund her mouth, nose and chin to fit the changes made in 1.
4. Removed her Scar since the changes i made lets it flow in the air or disapear :/
